    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    LookAndFeel
    The `LookAndFeel` enum represents the different look and feel of the application.
    Main
    The `Main` class represents the main class of the Sudoku.
    Sudoku
    The `Sudoku` class represents a Sudoku puzzle.
    SudokuPanel
    The `SudokuPanel` class represents the main panel for the Sudoku application.
    SudokuResolver
    The `SudokuResolver` class represents a Sudoku resolver.
    SudokuResolverBT
    The `SudokuResolverBT` class represents a Sudoku resolver using backtracking.
    SudokuResolverMixed
    The `SudokuResolverMixed` class represents a Sudoku resolver using a mixed method.
    SudokuResolverReduction
    The `SudokuResolverReduction` class represents a Sudoku resolver using reduction.
    SudokuSize
    The `SudokuSize` enum represents the size of the Sudoku.
    SudokuSymbols
    The `SudokuSymbols` enum represents the symbols of the Sudoku.
    SudokuTextInterface
    The `SudokuTextInterface` class represents the text interface of the Sudoku.
